23/05/2020

# Verbs and Simple Present

Verbos de exemplo:
speak, think, see

Pronomes:
I, you, we, they

I 	 speak english
I	 think too much
I 	 see dead people

you  speak english
you	 think too much		
you  see dead people	

we 	 speak english
we   think too much
we 	 see dead people

they speak english
they think too much
they see dead people

Os verbos em inglês não mudam quando são I/you/we/they no PRESENTE.

O unico caso que muda é quando usamos os pronomes:
he, she, it

He/She/It	 speaks english
He/She/It 	 thinks too much
He/She/It 	 sees dead people

Isso no PRESENTE!!! - SIMPLE PRESENT
===================
Eu falo inglês; Ele fala inglês; Eu corro; Eu penso; Eu vejo;

I 			run 	- Eu corro
You 		run		- Você/Vocês corre/correm
He/She/It 	runs	- Ele/Ela/Isto corre
We 			run		- Nós corremos
They 		run		- Eles correm




